data.description: Nestled in the heart of South Lakeland, this charming property is situated in a well-established neighborhood, offering the perfect blend of convenience and comfort. With 4 bedrooms and 2 baths, it's a delightful family home waiting for you to make it your own. The carport has been enclosed, creating a versatile bonus room that can effortlessly serve as a family room or a spacious 4th bedroom with a large closet. Imagine the possibilities – you could easily transform this space into a master ensuite by converting the existing laundry room and storage area into a combined bathroom and laundry room. The plumbing and electricity are already in place, making this a convenient and exciting opportunity for customization. Step into the heart of this home and discover a kitchen transformed by a contemporary color palette. The cabinets have been updated with a fresh, modern hue that breathes new life into the space. The kitchen, equipped with stainless steel appliances, seamlessly flows into a dining area with sliding glass doors leading to a screened and covered lanai. This outdoor oasis is an extension of the living area, perfect for relaxing or entertaining. Inside, you'll appreciate the luxury vinyl and tile flooring that extends throughout, creating a cohesive and low-maintenance living space. The interior has been freshly painted, ensuring a bright and welcoming atmosphere. One of the standout features of this property is the expansive, fully fenced backyard. It's a versatile canvas for your outdoor dreams, complete with a bountiful avocado tree, fire pit and a screened lanai that extends to a covered patio. Additionally, there's a 12 x 14 backyard storage building that has been thoughtfully insulated, equipped with electricity, and air-conditioned. This space is perfect for a man cave, a home office for remote workers, an exercise and workout room, or whatever suits your needs. An additional storage building in the backyard provides even more convenience. Other notable features include an EcoSmart Tankless water heater installed 2019, New Roof installed in 2018, New A/C in 2019 with a Smart Thermostat and New window blinds throughout. Also, an irrigation system in both the front and backyard and ample space in the backyard for a swimming pool if you desire. With no HOA to worry about, this property offers you the freedom to tailor it to your lifestyle. This property is conveniently situated 3.7 miles from Downtown Lakeland, offering proximity to coffee shops, shopping centers, entertainment venues, and excellent dining options. It's also within a 3 to 4-mile radius of various amenities, including dog parks, Lake Morton, Lake Mirror, Lake Hollingsworth, Dixieland, Lakeside Village Shopping, Cleveland Heights Golf Course, Lakeland Tennis Courts, Common Ground Park, Bonnet Springs Park, and much more! With easy access to Tampa and Orlando, thanks to its location just minutes from the Polk Parkway and I-4, this property ensures a seamless commute to all of Central Florida, including hospitals, airports, Walt Disney World, Legoland, other theme parks, and Florida's beautiful beaches! Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to call this South Lakeland gem your own. Contact us today to schedule a viewing and experience the endless possibilities this home has to offer.
